<H3> <TI>   Kim Yong-sam Condemned for Remarks on GATT </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK2402151694 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1502 GMT 24 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2402151694 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, February 24 (KCNA) -- The traitor Kim 
Yong-sam Monday decried the demand of people of all walks of 
life for another "Uruguay Round [UR] negotiation" concerning 
agricultural market opening, and ruled out the possibility of 
another negotiation, claiming that the demand came from 
ignorance of "diplomacy," according to a radio report from Seoul. 
  It was outrageous of the traitor to try to justify the 
kowtowing diplomacy and treacherous diplomacy yielding to the 
brigandish demands of foreign aggressors and call for accepting 
it. 
  He openly broke his "election commitment not to open the 
rice 
market" when it was still vivid in people's memory. This 
revealed once again the true color of the poor fellow who has 
prolonged his life with perfidy and treachery. 

