chair the group to be gathered under the banner of "Real 
Liberalism," they said. 
  The group's document states the purpose of the society 
basically adopts previous policies of the LDP, which surrendered 
its 38-year grip on power last August to the coalition 
government led by Prime Minister Morihiro Hosokawa. 

