<F P=100> Burma </F>
<H3> <TI>   PRC Border Inspection Delegation Arrives </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK2302162294 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 23 Feb 
94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2302162294 </F>
<F P=104>  Rangoon Radio Burma </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Burmese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An eight-member Chinese delegation led by Mr. (Zhou 
Mang Qian), survey department head from the Defense Ministry of 
the People's Republic of China arrived in Yangon [Rangoon] by 
air this afternoon to attend the fourth meeting of survey and 
mapping experts for the second Myanmar [Burma]-China joint 
border inspection. 

</TEXT>

