<F P=100> Burma </F>
<H3> <TI>   Indonesian Foreign Minister Departs 23 Feb </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK2302160294 Rangoon Radio Burma in Burmese 1330 GMT 23 Feb 
94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2302160294 </F>
<F P=104>  Rangoon Radio Burma </F>


