Party of Korea and the Korean people who leads the cause of 
socialism in the van with extraordinary wisdom, outstanding 
leadership ability and noble virtues. 
  "Comrade Kim Chong-il is greatly contributing to bringing 
about a worldwide upswing in the cause of socialism. 
