  [Excerpts] The Foreign Ministry has informed the Russian 
Embassy in Ljubljana that the escorts of Vladimir Zhirinovskiy, 
Russian Deputy and leader of the Liberal Democratic Party, 
grossly violated public order in Bled last night. [passage 
omitted]. 
