<H3> <TI>   Pawlak Reshuffles More Provincial Governors </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3101195194 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1644 GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD3101195194 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Polish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Warsaw, 31 Jan--The chairman of the Council of 
Ministers [Waldemar Pawlak] has made changes in top local state 
administration posts, the Government Press Office has reported. 
  The prime minister has recalled the following provincial 
governors as of 31 January: 
  Koszalin: Stanislaw Marian Socha 
