<H3> <TI>   HVO Reports Muslim Attacks </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3101135794 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in English 1303 
GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3101135794 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb Radio Croatia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] According to Croatian Defense Force [HVO] reports, 
Muslim forces in central Bosnia attacked parts of the Zepce 
front this morning. On the southern section of this front large 
deployments of Muslim troops were observed. On the 
Uskoplje-Rama front Muslim forces were also active, firing all 
along HVO lines. On the Mostar front Muslim forces have 
increased their attacks, firing with artillery and smallarms on 
the city, while several mortars hit the city center. Serb forces 
were active in the Orasje-Samac area, using small arms and heavy 
machineguns. 

</TEXT>

