<F P=103> AU0102142394 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Bulgarian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] On 1 February National Assembly Chairman Aleksandur 
Yordanov met Iranian Foreign Minister 'Ali Akbar Velayati, who 
is paying an official visit to Bulgaria. 
  The Iranian foreign minister agreed with Aleksandur 
Yordanov's opinion that the issue of the Bulgarian Muslims must 
be taken off the agenda of the Islamic Conference Organization, 
