<H3> <TI>   NATO Mission Arrives To Discuss `Partnership' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0102133594 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1105 
GMT 1 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0102133594 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network </F>


